summary: The diff implements a comprehensive Test Exam Report feature with tabular interface, backend CRUD operations, and admin management capabilities. All 7 requirements (REQ-14 through REQ-20) appear to be fully implemented with proper data models, role-based access control, sorting, formatting, and UI components matching the specified design.
